FBIS4-16564 "drsov074_a_94030" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 16 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS LDPR Denies Funding by Former E. German Party LDPR Denies Funding by Former E. German Party LD1604140594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1251 GMT 16 Apr 94 LD1604140594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent Andrey Timofeyev: "LDPR Official Denies BERLINER ZEITUNG Report that Zhirinovskiy's Election Campaign Was Financed by the Former Socialist Unity Party of Germany" -- ITAR-TASS headline] [Text] Moscow, 16 Apr -- The Liberal Democratic Party of Russia [LDPR] has not received any money from the former Socialist Unity Party of Germany in order to conduct an election campaign, Stanislav Zarichankiy, an official in the LDPR's organizational department, declared today in a conversation with an ITAR-TASS correspondent. "We know of no Berlin company called 'TFO,' which is supposed to have transferred money to the LDPR's funds," he said. "We regard this as an attempt by the German paper to mislead the public."
